---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="AI Automation for Engineering Teams" description="Brandon Woodward — Systems Architect & AI Automation Consultant. I help engineering teams cut manual ops and integrate AI tooling that actually works.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grain"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text">
          <div class="hero-eyebrow">Systems Architecture &amp; AI Automation</div>
          <h1>
            Stop running your team<br />
            on <em>manual work.</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
            I help engineering teams cut ops toil and integrate AI tooling into real workflows —
            not demos, not pilots. Systems that run in production.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Discovery Call &nbsp;→</a>
            <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">See Services</a>
          </div>
          <div class="social-proof">
            <span>20+ years engineering</span>
            <span class="rule">&nbsp;·&nbsp;</span>
            <span>Rackspace · Amazon · Salesforce GovCloud</span>
            <span class="rule">&nbsp;·&nbsp;</span>
            <span>FedRAMP-cleared environments</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 190" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- Low dome crown -->
            <path d="M 53 78 Q 51 24 100 22 Q 149 24 147 78" fill="#C9A87C" opacity="0.35"/>
            <!-- Wide flat brim -->
            <rect x="3" y="74" width="194" height="26" rx="8" fill="#C9A87C" opacity="0.35"/>
            <!-- Hat band -->
            <rect x="53" y="74" width="94" height="13" fill="#B5551A" opacity="0.38"/>
            <!-- Mustache right — wide sweep, upturned tips -->
            <path d="M 100 130 C 113 122 134 117 153 119 C 168 122 175 134 172 145 C 169 154 156 157 149 151 C 143 146 141 138 129 131 C 120 127 110 127 100 130 Z" fill="#B5551A" opacity="0.32"/>
            <!-- Mustache left -->
            <path d="M 100 130 C 87 122 66 117 47 119 C 32 122 25 134 28 145 C 31 154 44 157 51 151 C 57 146 59 138 71 131 C 80 127 90 127 100 130 Z" fill="#B5551A" opacity="0.32"/>
            <!-- Beard -->
            <path d="M 65 155 Q 100 175 135 155 Q 122 165 100 168 Q 78 165 65 155 Z" fill="#B5551A" opacity="0.22"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain points -->
  <section class="section pain-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Sound familiar?</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your team is capable.<br />Your systems are holding them back.</h2>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-num">01</div>
          <h3>Manual toil stealing sprint capacity</h3>
          <p>Your engineers are spending hours on deploys, incident response, and runbooks that should be automated. That time belongs in your roadmap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-num">02</div>
          <h3>AI that doesn't connect to your systems</h3>
          <p>You've tried AI tools. They work in isolation but don't plug into your actual infrastructure. You need architecture, not another SaaS subscription.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card pain-card">
          <div class="pain-num">03</div>
          <h3>Architecture decisions made without expertise</h3>
          <p>Hiring a senior systems architect full-time costs $250K+. You need that expertise for specific decisions, not a permanent headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What I do -->
  <section class="section what-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="what-inner">
        <div class="what-text">
          <div class="section-label">What I do</div>
          <h2>Architecture that runs.<br /><em>AI that earns its keep.</em></h2>
          <p>
            I design systems that automate real operational work — the CI/CD toil, the runbook
            theater, the alert noise — and integrate AI where it delivers measurable throughput,
            not where it looks impressive in a slide deck.
          </p>
          <p>
            My background spans infrastructure at Rackspace, AWS IAM, RDS, and a decade at
            Salesforce GovCloud building security tooling for FedRAMP environments. I write Go,
            Python, and Bash. I deploy with Terraform and Ansible. I've run Kubernetes at scale.
          </p>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">More about my background →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="what-stack">
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Languages</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Go</span><span class="tag">Python</span><span class="tag">Bash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Infrastructure</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Terraform</span><span class="tag">Ansible</span>
              <span class="tag">Kubernetes</span><span class="tag">Docker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Cloud &amp; Compliance</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">AWS</span><span class="tag">FedRAMP</span>
              <span class="tag">GovCloud</span><span class="tag">PKI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-card card">
            <div class="stack-label">Observability</div>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Prometheus</span><span class="tag">Grafana</span>
              <span class="tag">Alertmanager</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services preview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Engagements</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Three ways to work together.</h2>
      <div class="services-preview">
        <div class="card service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">Entry point</div>
          <h3>Discovery Audit</h3>
          <p>A deep-dive into your current systems. Walk away with a written report of automation opportunities and an AI integration roadmap.</p>
          <div class="service-price">From $2,000</div>
          <a href="/services#discovery" class="btn btn-outline service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-card service-card--featured">
          <div class="service-tier service-tier--accent">Most common</div>
          <h3>Project Engagement</h3>
          <p>Design and build one specific automation or AI integration — from architecture to production delivery.</p>
          <div class="service-price">$10,000–25,000</div>
          <a href="/services#project" class="btn btn-primary service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card service-card">
          <div class="service-tier">Ongoing</div>
          <h3>Advisory Retainer</h3>
          <p>Async architecture guidance and a monthly strategy call. Senior systems expertise on demand without the headcount.</p>
          <div class="service-price">$3,000/mo</div>
          <a href="/services#retainer" class="btn btn-outline service-btn">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <div class="cta-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 60 52" width="50" height="43" fill="none">
            <path d="M 16 21 Q 15 7 30 6 Q 45 7 44 21" fill="#C9A87C"/>
            <rect x="1" y="20" width="58" height="7" rx="2.5" fill="#C9A87C"/>
            <rect x="16" y="20" width="28" height="3.5" fill="#B5551A"/>
            <path d="M 30 36 C 34 33 41 31 47 32 C 52 33 55 38 53 43 C 51 47 46 48 43 45 C 40 42 39 38 34 35 C 32 34 31 34 30 36 Z" fill="#C9A87C"/>
            <path d="M 30 36 C 26 33 19 31 13 32 C 8 33 5 38 7 43 C 9 47 14 48 17 45 C 20 42 21 38 26 35 C 28 34 29 34 30 36 Z" fill="#C9A87C"/>
            <path d="M 20 46 Q 30 52 40 46 Q 36 49 30 50 Q 24 49 20 46 Z" fill="#C9A87C" opacity="0.6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Ready to automate what's slowing you down?</h2>
        <p>Start with a 30-minute conversation. No pitch deck. Just an honest look at where automation and AI can move the needle for your team.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Free Intro Call →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0 5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-lt);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-grain {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        89deg,
        transparent 0px, transparent 14px,
        rgba(160, 100, 40, 0.028) 14px, rgba(160, 100, 40, 0.028) 15px
      ),
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        91deg,
        transparent 0px, transparent 22px,
        rgba(140, 80, 20, 0.018) 22px, rgba(140, 80, 20, 0.018) 23px
      );
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-mark {
    opacity: 0.6;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .social-proof {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .rule { color: var(--border); }

  /* Pain */
  .pain-section {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-lt);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .pain-card { position: relative; }

  .pain-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pain-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .pain-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* What I do */
  .what-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-lt);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-lt);
  }

  .what-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .what-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .what-text h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .what-text p {
    color: var(--dim);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .what-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.9rem; }

  .stack-card { padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem; background: var(--surface2); }

  .stack-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

  .tag {
    background: rgba(181, 85, 26, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(181, 85, 26, 0.22);
    color: var(--accent2);
    padding: 0.18rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Services */
  .services-preview {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .service-card--featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent), 0 8px 32px rgba(181, 85, 26, 0.1);
    background: #F5E8D0;
  }

  .service-tier {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .service-tier--accent { color: var(--accent); }

  .service-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    flex: 1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .service-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }

  .service-btn {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-lt);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-mark { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-inner p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-mark { display: none; }
    .what-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .hero { padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem; }
  }
</style>
